----------------
-- cl-youtube --
----------------

* YoutTube objects *
  Creates CLOS representation of the YouTube API.

* XML output *
  The call to the REST API return an XML object.



** Version 0.1 **

* Implements the REST api for User informations *

    * youtube.users.get_profile
    * youtube.users.list_favorite_videos
    * youtube.users.list_friends

* Implements the REST api for Video Viewing *

    * youtube.videos.get_details
    * youtube.videos.list_by_tag (now with paging)
    * youtube.videos.list_by_user
    * youtube.videos.list_featured



